'''''Waithira''''', ni filime yo muri 2017 yo muri [[Kenya]]- Amajyepfo [[Afurika|y’Africa]] yerekana ubuzima bwa film yerekanwe na Eva Njoki Munyiri kandi yafatanije n’umuyobozi ubwe hamwe na Stefan Gieren na Jean Meeran muri Team Tarbaby<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt7937958/</ref>.<ref>https://junofilms.com/req.php?req=static.php&page=waithira</ref>  Iyi filime ivuga ku mateka y’umuyobozi Eva Njoki Munyiri n’amasangano yayo n'amateka yibagiwe ya [[Kenya]], umuco wa pop na diaspora<ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2018/10/ndiva-womens-film-festival-2018_94.html</ref>. 

Waithira yakiriwe neza kandi yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://africasacountry.com/2017/07/how-do-you-write-about-a-flawed-film</ref>.  Hari screened mikuru nka DIFF y'Epfo & guhura, Iserukiramuco rya Filime Nyafurika, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Créteil, n'ibindi  Muri 2018, iyi filime yari ihagarariwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ry'inyandiko rya Munich<ref>https://rushlake-africa.com/portfolio-items/waithira/</ref>.<ref>https://www.the-star.co.ke/sasa/lifestyle/2019-09-21-waithira-a-family-documentary-and-account-of-our-national-heritage/</ref> 

